hotelList.name: The Maxwell Hotel - A Piece of Pineapple Hospitality
hotelList.localizedName: The Maxwell Hotel - A Piece of Pineapple Hospitality
hotelList.nonLocalizedName: The Maxwell Hotel - A Piece of Pineapple Hospitality
hotelList.shortDescription: Located in Downtown Seattle, this boutique hotel is steps from Pacific Northwest Ballet and Marion Oliver McCaw Hall. Seattle Center and Experience Music Project Museum are also within 10 minutes.

hotelList.name: Hotel Andra
hotelList.shortDescription: This family-friendly Seattle hotel is located in a shopping district, within a 10-minute walk of Westlake Center and Pike Place Market. Space Needle and Seattle Great Wheel are also within 15 minutes.

hotelList.name: Hotel FIVE - A Piece of Pineapple Hospitality
hotelList.localizedName: Hotel FIVE - A Piece of Pineapple Hospitality
hotelList.nonLocalizedName: Hotel FIVE - A Piece of Pineapple Hospitality
hotelList.shortDescription: Featuring a funky, modern style, this Seattle hotel is in the hip Belltown neighborhood,5 blocks from Pacific Place and Westlake Center shops. The Space Needle, Experience Music Project, and Pacific Science Center are within 6 blocks.

hotelList.name: Mediterranean Inn
hotelList.shortDescription: Set in the Lower Queen Anne neighborhood, this hotel is 2 blocks from Seattle Center and 1 mile from Pike Place Market and downtown Seattle. Terminal 91 Cruise Facility is 1.5 miles from the hotel.

hotelList.name: Mayflower Park Hotel
hotelList.shortDescription: Built in 1927, this 12-story hotel is connected by walkway to Westlake Center shops and by monorail to the Space Needle; Pike Place Market and Benaroya Hall are 4 blocks away.

hotelList.name: Fairmont Olympic Hotel
hotelList.shortDescription: Built on the original site of the University of Washington, this grand hotel is just a few blocks from the Seattle Art Museum, Pacific Place shops, the Pike Place Market, and the convention center.

hotelList.name: Thompson Seattle
hotelList.shortDescription: Located in Downtown Seattle, this hotel is steps from Original Starbucks and Pike Place Market. Seattle Great Wheel and Washington State Convention Center are also within 15 minutes.

hotelList.name: Best Western Executive Inn
hotelList.shortDescription: Located within 2 blocks of the Seattle Center, the downtown monorail, and the towering Space Needle, this hotel is a mile from Seattle's world-famous Pike Place Market.

hotelList.name: The Paramount Hotel
hotelList.shortDescription: This 11-story hotel is one block from the Paramount Theater, Pacific Place shops, or the Washington State Convention Center, and 3 blocks from Westlake Center.

hotelList.name: Hotel Max, A Provenance Hotel
hotelList.shortDescription: Hotel Max is in downtown Seattle, 6 blocks from Pike Place Market and 1 mile from Capitol Hill. Pacific Place shopping is a block away.

hotelList.name: Pan Pacific Seattle
hotelList.shortDescription: This Seattle hotel is situated above a Whole Foods Market on the edge of downtown, 4 blocks from downtown shopping, a half mile from Seattle Center and within a mile of Pike Place Market. The New Chihully Museum of Glass is also within easy reach.

hotelList.name: Motif Seattle
hotelList.shortDescription: Located in Downtown Seattle, this hotel is within a 10-minute walk of 5th Avenue Theater, Pike Place Market, and Washington State Convention Center. Columbia Center and Seattle Great Wheel are also within 10 minutes.

hotelList.name: The Loyal Inn
hotelList.shortDescription: This Seattle hotel is less than a half-mile from Pike Place Market, the Space Needle, and the Key Arena.

hotelList.name: The Roosevelt, A Provenance Hotel
hotelList.shortDescription: Built in 1929, this 20-story Seattle hotel is across from Pacific Place shopping, one block from the Washington State Convention & Trade Center, less than 1 mile (1.6 kilometers)from Seattle Ferry Terminal, and two blocks from the Paramount Theater.

hotelList.name: Grand Hyatt Seattle
hotelList.shortDescription: This 30-story downtown Seattle hotel is two blocks from the upscale Pacific Place Mall and within seven blocks of cultural attractions. The hotel is adjacent to the Washington State Convention Center.

hotelList.name: Hyatt House Seattle/Downtown
hotelList.shortDescription: Located in Downtown Seattle, this hotel is steps from Science Fiction Museum and Hall of Fame, Space Needle, and Experience Music Project Museum. Seattle Center and Marion Oliver McCaw Hall are also within 10 minutes.

hotelList.name: MarQueen Hotel
hotelList.shortDescription: Occupying a handsomely restored 1918 building, this boutique hotel is nestled among restaurants, theaters, and shops in the vibrant Queen Anne neighborhood, 2 blocks from the Seattle Center.

hotelList.name: Four Seasons Hotel Seattle
hotelList.shortDescription: Offering modern luxury in an ideal downtown setting, Four Seasons Hotel Seattle is across from the Seattle Art Museum, 1 block from the Pike Place Market, and a five-minute walk from the waterfront.

hotelList.name: Inn at the Market
hotelList.shortDescription: Located within downtown Seattle's historic Pike Place Market and surrounded by shops and cafés, Inn at the Market sits on a cobblestone street overlooking picturesque Elliott Bay and Puget Sound.

hotelList.name: The Edgewater - A Noble House Hotel
hotelList.localizedName: The Edgewater - A Noble House Hotel
hotelList.nonLocalizedName: The Edgewater - A Noble House Hotel
hotelList.shortDescription: Extending over Elliott Bay from Pier 67, this 1962 landmark is adjacent to the Bell Harbor Conference Center and less than a mile from the Pike Place Market and the Space Needle.

hotelList.name: Travelodge By The Space Needle
hotelList.shortDescription: This smoke-free Seattle hotel is located 2 blocks from the Space Needle, Experience Music Project, and Seattle Center.

hotelList.name: Watertown Hotel - A Piece of Pineapple Hospitality
hotelList.localizedName: Watertown Hotel - A Piece of Pineapple Hospitality
hotelList.nonLocalizedName: Watertown Hotel - A Piece of Pineapple Hospitality
hotelList.shortDescription: This hotel is 4 blocks from the University of Washington and 4 miles from downtown Seattle; Gasworks Park, University Village shopping, and UW Husky Stadium are 1 mile away.

hotelList.name: Palladian, a Kimpton Hotel
hotelList.shortDescription: Located in Downtown Seattle, this eco-friendly hotel is within a 5-minute walk of Original Starbucks and Pike Place Market. Space Needle and Seattle Great Wheel are also within 1 mi (2 km).

hotelList.name: Alexis Hotel, a Kimpton Hotel
hotelList.shortDescription: This downtown Seattle charmer is in a historic building 1 block east of the waterfront and ferry terminal, and 4 blocks from Pike Place Market and Pioneer Square.

hotelList.name: Warwick Seattle Hotel
hotelList.shortDescription: The 19-story hotel is located in downtown Seattle's hip Belltown neighborhood, 2 blocks from the Monorail and 5 blocks from the Seattle waterfront and Pike Place Market.
